      "message": "System property is not the right way to do this. Since it controls more system wide properties like whether the phone is a cdma phone or not.\n\nAlso I don\u0027t know why we need a property ? We should just have the API always. Applications can decide whether they want to use it or not and give the choice if needed to the users via some Settings UI\n\nOur APIs shouldn\u0027t be based on some setting to enable or disable them.",
